				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Well, I don't know of any rope pattern, but what I think you mean is a silk cord.  This can be made by first combining two spiderling silks to make silk thread.  Then combine 3 silk threads (unstacked) and you will get a silk cord (if you succeed that is!).  Silk cords can then be combined with low quality pelts to make tailored bags.  Hope this helps!
				</font>
